    <title>Worked Example: For Loops - Counter</title>
    <xi:include href='./subgoals-loops.ptx' /> 
    <subsection>   
    <p>You can watch this video or read through the content below it.</p>

    <video xml:id="video-loops-we2" youtube="8j6dUuJaVnU" width="auto"/>
    <p>Problem: Given the following code, what is the output?</p>
    <program language="java">
        <input>
total = 0;
for (int x = 5; x &lt; 50; x++)
{
  if (x % 5 == 0)
     total += x;
}
System.out.println(total);
        </input>
    </program>
</subsection>
