    <subsection>
        <title>SG3: Trace the loop</title>
        <figure align="">
            <image source="Loops/Figures/WL1A-ForCounter.png" width="50%" alt="Counter"/>
        </figure>
        <figure align="">
            <image source="Loops/Figures/WL1ASlide6.png" width="25%" alt="Counter"/>
        </figure>
        <p>X increments by 1, but the value is only added to total when it is evenly divisible by 5.</p>
        <p>Notice that this example gives the equivalent <c>for</c> loop for the <c>while</c> loop in 6.1.</p>
    
        <answer>
            <p>Output is 225</p>
        </answer>
